<p>
<note n="0494003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0494003">唯＝有【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0494004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0494004">（答）＋若【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0495001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0495001">說＝誦【三】【宮】</note>
